 224:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/gps/minmea.h **** /**
 225:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/gps/minmea.h ****  * Scanf-like processor for NMEA sentences. Supports the following formats:
 226:SynaptiX_FDK/components/modules/gps/minmea.h ****  * c - single character (char *)
